Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.78,0:03:08.75,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君の邪魔をしたいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.86,0:03:11.64,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,独りよがりでいいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.74,0:03:15.95,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木を隠すなら森だっていうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.47,0:03:20.35,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ミスダイブから始め
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.51,0:03:23.29,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出会いなおすのもいいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.42,0:03:27.86,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時系列を敵に回そう
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.54,0:03:34.04,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強さだけが武器じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.76,0:03:40.68,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,その意味を今　教えてくれたね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.82,0:03:46.04,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君に見せたいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.68,0:03:53.27,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,この向こう側にあるものを
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.72,0:03:56.01,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風が強い
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.31,0:03:59.18,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君にも分かるはず
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.26,0:04:03.64,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僕は飛べないさ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.11,0:04:10.69,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分け合えるなんて甘えたら
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.86,0:04:13.59,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,さぁ　この手を取れ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.20,0:04:16.40,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貫くなら　
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.40,0:04:18.32,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,さぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,OP-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.78,0:03:08.75,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要干扰你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.86,0:03:11.64,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我自以为是好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.74,0:03:15.95,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有说「藏木于林」的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.47,0:03:20.35,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从小小的错误开始
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.51,0:03:23.29,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重头来过也好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.42,0:03:27.86,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以时间数列包围敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.54,0:03:34.04,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是只有坚强才是武器
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.76,0:03:40.68,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在 你教会了我这句话的含义
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.82,0:03:46.04,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想让你也看到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.68,0:03:53.27,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那彼方的风景
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.72,0:03:56.01,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风很大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.31,0:03:59.18,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该也明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.26,0:04:03.64,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会飞的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.11,0:04:10.69,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若撒娇便能相互分享
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.86,0:04:13.59,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 牵着我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.20,0:04:16.40,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定能坚持到底
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.40,0:04:18.32,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,OP-CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠い光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霧の夜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闇にとらわれる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,気配 抱いて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,それは
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻の
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花びら
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ゆっくりと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離れてゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何が為だ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,この空の扉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷鳴を 感じる心は
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,響かせるの　心は
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そう 彼方へ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小さい光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远方之光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白雾之夜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囚于黑暗之中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥抱着的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻影中的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花瓣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渐渐地
